{\"data\":[{\"keyName\":\"通用\",\"manualContentBeans\":[{\"title\":\"1、首页\",\"content\":\"滑动查看卡片，点击卡片可以进入到应用内；多媒体卡片点击可选择音源，卡片上支持快捷操作，如导航搜索、音乐暂停；支持自定义卡片顺序，长按卡片3S后，按住拖动可调节卡片排序。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"ty_sy1\"},{\"imageResId\":\"ty_sy2\"}]},{\"title\":\"2、控制中心\",\"content\":\"可开启隐私模式，快速连接蓝牙、链接WIFI；打开360全景影像；回家/上班随时导航；你可以一键开启浪漫模式、雾霾模式、呵护宝宝、停车模式。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"ty_kzzx\"}]}]},{\"keyName\":\"语音\",\"manualContentBeans\":[{\"title\":\"1、语音查询周边\",\"content\":\"可以通过语音查询附近的停车场、美食、酒店、景点，示例说法：帮我查询附近的美食，图片以美食相关页面举例展示。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"yy_yyczb1\"},{\"imageResId\":\"yy_yyczb2\"}]},{\"title\":\"2、语音创建日程\",\"content\":\"可通过语音创建日程，示例说法：提醒我今天8点打电话给林楠楠告诉她直接去会议大厦。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"yy_yycjrc\"}]},{\"title\":\"3、语音查询天气/股票/百科\",\"content\":\"可通过语音查询天气/股票/百科等信息，示例说法：今天天气怎么样/百度的股票是多少/周杰伦是谁。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"yy_yycxtq\"},{\"imageResId\":\"yy_yycxgp\"},{\"imageResId\":\"yy_yycxbk\"}]},{\"title\":\"4、通用语音\",\"content\":\"支持语音免唤醒控制常用操作，如打开音乐/电台、播放歌曲、打开导航；\\r\\n支持语音唤醒控制系统常用设置，如打开蓝牙、声音大一点、屏幕亮一点、关屏等。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"yy_tyyy\"}]}]},{\"keyName\":\"导航\",\"manualContentBeans\":[{\"title\":\"1、基础导航\",\"content\":\"支持搜索目的地、查看周边、导航算路、路线引导。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"dh_jcdh1\"},{\"imageResId\":\"dh_jcdh2\"},{\"imageResId\":\"dh_jcdh3\"},{\"imageResId\":\"dh_jcdh4\"}]},{\"title\":\"2、语音导航\",\"content\":\"支持语音发起导航/查询路况，你可以说：你好，风神，我要去人民广场；\\r\\n你好，风神，去人民广场要多久。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"dh_yydh1\"},{\"imageResId\":\"dh_yydh2\"}]}]},{\"keyName\":\"多媒体\",\"manualContentBeans\":[{\"title\":\"1、音乐\",\"content\":\"用户使用音乐播放器，可播放来自U盘，网络，本地和蓝牙的歌曲，可查看歌曲播放列表，切换播放模式，并对歌曲进行收藏，查看歌手其他的歌等。同时支持语音控制功能。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"dmt_yy1\"},{\"imageResId\":\"dmt_yy2\"},{\"imageResId\":\"dmt_yy3\"}]},{\"title\":\"2、有声\",\"content\":\"用户使用有声，可切换网络电台或收音机。针对收音机可使用听歌识曲，轮播搜台，收藏电台等功能。针对有声，用户可浏览收听各种节目，可登陆喜马拉雅账户实现订阅，付费精品查看等功能。同时支持语音控制功能。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"dmt_ys1\"},{\"imageResId\":\"dmt_ys2\"},{\"imageResId\":\"dmt_ys3\"},{\"imageResId\":\"dmt_ys4\"}]}]},{\"keyName\":\"电话\",\"manualContentBeans\":[{\"title\":\"1、电话\",\"content\":\"在电话应用中你可以同步手机通讯录信息，搜索联系人，可通过语音或界面操作进行电话的接听，挂断，拨打。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"dh_dh\"}]}]},{\"keyName\":\"车辆\",\"manualContentBeans\":[{\"title\":\"1、空调\",\"content\":\"支持中控屏操作控制空调，支持语音控制空调，你可以说：\\r\\n你好，风神，温度调到25度\\r\\n你好，风神，风大一点\\r\\n你好，风神，我冷了\\r\\n你好，风神，车里有点闷。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"cl_kt\"}]},{\"title\":\"2、情景模式\",\"content\":\"支持8种情景模式的选择。车里有宝宝，可以开启“呵护宝宝”；空气质量差，可以 开启“雾霾模式”；快到目的地时，可以用“停车模式”一键完成停车前的准备，你可以语音打开/关闭情景模式，如：你好，风神，打开呵护宝宝模式。考虑到安全性，打开雨雪模式、雾霾模式、呵护宝宝模式需要您手动关闭车窗和天窗。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"cl_qjms\"}]},{\"title\":\"3、车况&保养\",\"content\":\"可以查看近7天的平均油耗数据；你可以关注到爱车的保养周期和保养历史。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"cl_ckby1\"},{\"imageResId\":\"cl_ckby2\"}]}]},{\"keyName\":\"购买服务\",\"manualContentBeans\":[{\"title\":\"1、账单\",\"content\":\"在账单中可查看在车机上产生的订单信息，可支付相应的订单。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"gmfw_zd\"}]},{\"title\":\"2、流量\",\"content\":\"可查询当前流量使用情况，流量不足时还可以购买流量包。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"gmfw_ll\"}]},{\"title\":\"3、违章查询\",\"content\":\"可查询当前车辆违章信息。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"gmfw_wzcx\"}]}]},{\"keyName\":\"图片\",\"manualContentBeans\":[{\"title\":\"1、图片\",\"content\":\"支持查看U盘中的图片，你也可以将图片设置为首页第一张卡的背景。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"tp_tp\"}]}]},{\"keyName\":\"视频\",\"manualContentBeans\":[{\"title\":\"1、视频\",\"content\":\"支持查看U盘中的视频，开车过程中请勿开启视频，注意行车安全。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"sp_sp\"}]}]},{\"keyName\":\"设置\",\"manualContentBeans\":[{\"title\":\"1、设置\",\"content\":\"在设置中你可以对网络、车辆、显示、语音、音效、推荐开关的功能进行相应的控制操作，在系统设置中还可对系统进行升级，以获得最新的车机体验。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"sz_yx\"}]}]},{\"keyName\":\"航旅\",\"manualContentBeans\":[{\"title\":\"1、航旅\",\"content\":\"你可以通过语音或界面依据航班号或机场来查询相应信息，可通过扫码登陆航旅纵横账户，同步个人飞行计划；可对相应航班进行关注，关注的航班若发生状态变更，会收到相应的提示。\",\"contentImages\":[{\"imageResId\":\"ly_fxjh\"},{\"imageResId\":\"ly_wd\"},{\"imageResId\":\"ly_sshb\"}]}]}]}

Dongfeng Motor Corporation prioritizes the safeguarding of your personal data and privacy rights. While using Dongfeng Box, the vehicle may gather certain data as necessitated by its functionalities, which will be securely stored within the vehicle. Rest assured, Dongfeng Motor Corporation will not be able to access the data collected within the vehicle, except with your explicit consent in specific circumstances.

"You are strongly advised against independently repairing, selling, or disposing of vehicles or parts unless you visit the OEM's point-of-sale locations. To safeguard your legal rights and interests, it's highly recommended to proactively delete and wipe any sensitive data associated with the vehicles or parts in advance if you opt not to go to the OEM's point-of-sale locations for this purpose."

"For the security of your sensitive data, please ensure its deletion before visiting the OEM's point-of-sale locations for disposal or contact us for an enhanced solution regarding the recycling process at these locations. Additionally, kindly delete any sensitive data after using a vehicle that isn't yours to protect your legitimate data rights and interests."
We want to share the following privacy notice with you:

"1. Vehicle Camera: Dongfeng Box boasts six strategically placed cameras, one each on the front and rear bumpers, two on the side view mirrors, one on the A-pillar, and another on the front windshield. These cameras serve distinct purposes: one for the Driver Monitor System (DMS), which alerts for signs of distracted or impaired driving; another for the Front Camera Module (FCM), responsible for detecting distance and speed of vehicles ahead and automatically applying brakes when necessary; and the remaining four contribute to the 360° panoramic view, offering a comprehensive depiction of the vehicle's surroundings. Importantly, none of these cameras store video or biometric data; instead, they solely provide real-time camera footage of the vehicle's surroundings and radar perception results."

"2. Emergency Call(E-Call): E-Call is a vital service tailored to swiftly summon emergency assistance in the event of a road accident or upon activation of the SOS button. It is designed to protect people from accidents. When an accident happens, the Minimum Set of Data (MSD), including the vehicle's location, Vehicle Identification Number (VIN), vehicle direction, timestamp, and so on, will be directly transmitted to the local rescue institute."

"3. Front Camera Module (FCM): The FCM can reduce the collision risks in challenging driving conditions. In navigating the intricate driving environment, the vehicle's Autonomous Emergency Braking (AEB) and Front Collision Warning (FCW) functions play a crucial role by issuing collision alerts and adjusting speed or applying brakes to avert accidents. Similarly, Lane Keeping Assist (LKA) and Lane Departure Warning (LDW) systems identify lanes, aiding in accurate route navigation and providing departure warnings. Intelligent Speed Assistance (ISA) and Traffic Sign Recognition (TSR) functions recognize traffic signs, offering speed limit notifications and other relevant traffic information. Furthermore, Adaptive Cruiser Control (ACC) assists vehicles in maintaining a safe following distance and adhering to speed limits. It's important to note that the FCM system utilizes personal data solely for function activation and does not transmit any personal data back to us."

"4. Bluetooth Capabilities: To enhance convenience, you may connect Bluetooth to sync your contacts and retain your call history with the vehicle. It's crucial to emphasize that you retain complete control over this data, which remains securely stored within your vehicle at all times."

"5. Diagnostic Data: When vehicle repairs are necessary, you may be required to transmit diagnostic data such as the VIN, vehicle status, driving status, time, and driving mileage to designated recipients. Prior to sharing your personal data, it's essential to carefully review the privacy notice provided by the designated recipients to ensure your data is handled appropriately."
6. Navigation data: To comply with legal requirements, the vehicle gathers local weather conditions and its location data to determine the speed limit on roads.

"It's noteworthy that you maintain substantial control over the data collection and usage within the vehicle, including aspects such as device connections, hardware activation, and the enabling of driver assistance systems."
